      • create

        public ExtendedCompiler create()
        Crates a new instance of the ExtendedCompiler. If you do not set some specific implementations explicitly, then the following default ones are used:
        • LessCompilerImpl
        • SourceModificationDateBasedExpirationChecker
        • SourceFactory created by SourceFactoryBuilder with standard factories ( SourceFactoryBuilder.withStandard())
        • LessImportResolverImpl
        • LessImportReplacerImpl
        • DoNothingPostCompilationProcessor
        Returns:
        the new instance of the ExtendedCompiler.
        Since:
        1.0
